snippet.title: NEON TRAILER | Game Week 2019 ISART Digital
snippet.description:
Néon is a game we made for the Game Week 2019 at ISART Digital.

It was made in 5 days with a team of 8 people. The team was made of 1 game designer, 4 game artists, 1 sound designer, and 2 programmers.

You can download the game on Itch.io
